  "body_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n<title>Comeketo Catering - Ballpark Quote</title>\n</head>\n<body style=\"margin:0;padding:0;background-color:#f4f4f4;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">\n\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"background-color:#f4f4f4;padding:24px 0;\">\n<tr><td align=\"center\">\n\n<table width=\"620\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"max-width:620px;width:100%;background-color:#ffffff;border-radius:8px;overflow:hidden;\">\n\n  <tr>\n    <td bgcolor=\"#1a1a1a\" align=\"center\" style=\"background-color:#1a1a1a;padding:24px 32px;\">\n      <img src=\"https://comeketocatering.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/LOGO_WEB.png\" alt=\"Comeketo Catering\" width=\"160\" style=\"display:block;border:0;\">\n    </td>\n  </tr>\n\n  <tr>\n    <td style=\"padding:32px;color:#222222;\">\n\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 16px;font-size:16px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#222222;\">\n        Hi Monica! 👋\n      </p>\n\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 8px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#444444;\">\n        I put together a fun ballpark for your <strong>June 12, 2027</strong> wedding ✨\n      </p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 8px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#444444;\">\n        Just so I understand where things stand, are you mostly trying to get clarity on budget, menu direction, or service style right now?\n      </p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 24px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#444444;\">\n        Either way, I wanted to put some real numbers in front of you based on <strong>150 guests</strong> so this stops feeling abstract and starts feeling like a real decision 🍽️\n      </p>\n\n      <table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"margin-bottom:28px;\">\n        <tr>\n          <td bgcolor=\"#ff4b00\" style=\"background-color:#ff4b00;border-radius:5px;padding:11px 22px;\">\n            <a href=\"https://rawdre.github.io/comeketo-menu-landing/#packages\" style=\"color:#ffffff;font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:none;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">🔥 Explore the Full Menu Calculator</a>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n      </table>\n\n      <table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"margin-bottom:20px;border:1px solid #e8e8e8;border-radius:8px;overflow:hidden;\">\n        <tr>\n          <td bgcolor=\"#1a1a1a\" style=\"background-color:#1a1a1a;padding:13px 20px;\">\n            <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#ffffff;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">🔥 Option 1 — Brazilian BBQ (Churrasco)</p>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" style=\"background-color:#f9f9f9;padding:9px 20px;border-bottom:1px solid #e8e8e8;\">\n            <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:13px;color:#666666;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">On-site grilling with our team — the real deal! &nbsp;|&nbsp; 2 meats, 3 sides, and 1 salad</p>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td style=\"padding:16px 20px;\">\n            <table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\">\n              <tr>\n                <td style=\"padding:7px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0f0;font-size:14px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#333333;\">Food ($36.90 × 150 guests)</td>\n                <td align=\"right\" style=\"padding:7px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0f0;font-size:14px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#333333;font-weight:500;\">$5535.00</td>\n              </tr>\n              <tr>\n                <td style=\"padding:7px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0f0;font-size:14px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#333333;\">Appetizers</td>\n                <td align=\"right\" style=\"padding:7px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0f0;font-size:14px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#333333;font-weight:500;\">$0.00</td>\n              </tr>\n              <tr>\n                <td style=\"padding:7px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0f0;font-size:14px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#333333;\">MA Tax (7%)</td>\n                <td align=\"right\" style=\"padding:7px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0f0;font-size:14px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#333333;font-weight:500;\">$387.45</td>\n              </tr>\n              <tr>\n                <td style=\"padding:7px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0f0;font-size:14px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#333333;\">Service, Fuel &amp; Admin (24%)</td>\n                <td align=\"right\" style=\"padding:7px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0f0;font-size:14px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#333333;font-weight:500;\">$1328.40</td>\n              </tr>\n              <tr>\n                <td style=\"padding:7px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0f0;font-size:14px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#333333;\">Service Charge (over 50 guests at $3/pp)</td>\n                <td align=\"right\" style=\"padding:7px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0f0;font-size:14px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#333333;font-weight:500;\">$450.00</td>\n              </tr>\n              <tr>\n                <td style=\"padding:12px 0 6px;font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#1a1a1a;\">Ballpark Total</td>\n                <td align=\"right\" style=\"padding:12px 0 6px;font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#1a1a1a;\">~$7700.85</td>\n              </tr>\n            </table>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n      </table>\n\n      <table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"margin-bottom:24px;border:1px solid #e8e8e8;border-radius:8px;overflow:hidden;\">\n        <tr>\n          <td bgcolor=\"#1a1a1a\" style=\"background-color:#1a1a1a;padding:13px 20px;\">\n            <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#ffffff;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">🍽️ Option 2 — Deluxe Churrasco</p>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" style=\"background-color:#f9f9f9;padding:9px 20px;border-bottom:1px solid #e8e8e8;\">\n            <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:13px;color:#666666;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">One extra protein, fuller spread &nbsp;|&nbsp; 3 meats, 3 sides, and 1 salad</p>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td style=\"padding:16px 20px;\">\n            <table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\">\n              <tr>\n                <td style=\"padding:7px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0f0;font-size:14px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#333333;\">Food ($41.90 × 150 guests)</td>\n                <td align=\"right\" style=\"padding:7px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0f0;font-size:14px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#333333;font-weight:500;\">$6285.00</td>\n              </tr>\n              <tr>\n                <td style=\"padding:7px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0f0;font-size:14px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#333333;\">Appetizers</td>\n                <td align=\"right\" style=\"padding:7px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0f0;font-size:14px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#333333;font-weight:500;\">$0.00</td>\n              </tr>\n              <tr>\n                <td style=\"padding:7px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0f0;font-size:14px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#333333;\">MA Tax (7%)</td>\n                <td align=\"right\" style=\"padding:7px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0f0;font-size:14px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#333333;font-weight:500;\">$439.95</td>\n              </tr>\n              <tr>\n                <td style=\"padding:7px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0f0;font-size:14px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#333333;\">Service, Fuel &amp; Admin (24%)</td>\n                <td align=\"right\" style=\"padding:7px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0f0;font-size:14px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#333333;font-weight:500;\">$1508.40</td>\n              </tr>\n              <tr>\n                <td style=\"padding:7px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0f0;font-size:14px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#333333;\">Service Charge (over 50 guests at $3/pp)</td>\n                <td align=\"right\" style=\"padding:7px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0f0;font-size:14px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#333333;font-weight:500;\">$450.00</td>\n              </tr>\n              <tr>\n                <td style=\"padding:12px 0 6px;font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#1a1a1a;\">Ballpark Total</td>\n                <td align=\"right\" style=\"padding:12px 0 6px;font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#1a1a1a;\">~$8683.35</td>\n              </tr>\n            </table>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n      </table>\n\n      <table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"margin-bottom:22px;\">\n        <tr>\n          <td bgcolor=\"#fff8f0\" style=\"background-color:#fff8f0;border:1px solid #ffe0c0;border-radius:8px;padding:16px 20px;\">\n            <p style=\"margin:0 0 8px;font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#cc4400;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">🌟 Make It Your Own!</p>\n            <p style=\"margin:0 0 4px;font-size:14px;color:#555555;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">🧀 Appetizers — available to add on</p>\n            <p style=\"margin:0 0 4px;font-size:14px;color:#555555;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">🍰 Desserts — available to add on</p>\n            <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:14px;color:#555555;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">🥩 Extra proteins and sides — available to customize</p>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n      </table>\n\n      <table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"margin-bottom:22px;\">\n        <tr>\n          <td bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" style=\"background-color:#f9f9f9;border-radius:6px;padding:12px 16px;\">\n            <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:13px;color:#666666;line-height:1.8;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">\n              🥩 Default steak: <strong>Top Sirloin</strong> &nbsp;|&nbsp; 🍗 Default chicken: <strong>Chicken Wrapped in Bacon</strong> 🔥<br>\n              🍪 Complimentary cookies are included too. Ask me how to get this.\n            </p>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n      </table>\n\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 8px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#333333;\">\n        These are ballpark numbers so I can point you in the right direction without leading you the wrong way before we lock in your final guest count, menu, and service details 😊\n      </p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 28px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#333333;\">\n        <strong>Which option feels closer to what you want for the wedding?</strong>\n      </p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 24px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#333333;\">\n        If it helps, we could also jump on a quick call at 10:00 AM, 11:00 AM, or 1:00 PM.\n      </p>\n\n      <table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"margin-bottom:28px;\">\n        <tr><td style=\"border-top:1px solid #eeeeee;font-size:0;line-height:0;\">&nbsp;</td></tr>\n      </table>\n\n      <div style=\"margin:28px 0 0;padding:22px 24px;border-radius:24px;background:linear-gradient(180deg,#fff7ed 0%,#fff1f2 100%);border:1px solid #fed7aa;\">\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 10px;font-size:24px;font-weight:800;color:#7c2d12;\">🍽️ Come Taste It First</p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;color:#7c2d12;\">If tasting makes more sense, I can save you a spot so you can experience the food before deciding from a distance.</p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;color:#431407;line-height:1.6;\">\n        <strong>Date:</strong> Sunday, May 3<br />\n        <strong>Location:</strong> 199 Main St, Fitchburg, MA 01420<br />\n        <strong>Time:</strong> 5:30 PM<br />\n        <strong>Code:</strong> ANDRE\n      </p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 16px;color:#7c2d12;\">Seats are limited, so if you want in, reserve early.</p>\n      <div style=\"margin:0 0 16px;\">\n        <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1V2glKcSbQUtDes3Cuk7Q4bFPiazU1NwT/view\" style=\"display:inline-block;padding:12px 18px;background:#f59e0b;color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;border-radius:999px;font-weight:700;margin:0 10px 10px 0;\">Tasting Preview</a>\n        <a href=\"https://form.jotform.com/260145767354461\" style=\"display:inline-block;padding:12px 18px;background:#111827;color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;border-radius:999px;font-weight:700;margin:0 10px 10px 0;\">Tasting Registration</a>\n      </div>\n      <p style=\"margin:0;color:#7c2d12;\">The last tasting was a blast, and I would rather let them experience it than guess from a distance.</p>\n    </div>\n\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 4px;font-size:14px;color:#444444;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Regards,</p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 4px;font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;color:#1a1a1a;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Andre Raw</p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 4px;font-size:14px;color:#444444;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Catering Event Coordinator</p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 4px;font-size:14px;color:#444444;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">📲 C: (978) 235-3791 &nbsp;|&nbsp; 📲 W: (978) 381-1212</p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:13px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">\n        <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/comeketocatering\" style=\"color:#ff4b00;text-decoration:none;\">Facebook</a> &nbsp;|&nbsp;\n        <a href=\"https://instagram.com/comeketocatering\" style=\"color:#ff4b00;text-decoration:none;\">Instagram</a> &nbsp;|&nbsp;\n        <a href=\"https://comeketocatering.com\" style=\"color:#ff4b00;text-decoration:none;\">Website</a>\n      </p>\n\n    </td>\n  </tr>\n\n  <tr>\n    <td bgcolor=\"#1a1a1a\" align=\"center\" style=\"background-color:#1a1a1a;padding:14px 32px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:12px;color:#888888;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">\n        Comeketo Catering &nbsp;|&nbsp; 199 Main St, Fitchburg, MA 01420 &nbsp;|&nbsp; comeketocatering.com\n      </p>\n    </td>\n  </tr>\n\n</table>\n\n</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n\n  <div style=\"margin:26px 0 0;color:#432818;font-size:16px;line-height:1.65;\">\n    <p>From our call, what stood out to me is that you are not looking for a traditional plated setup. It sounds like you are leaning more toward a free-flow, hand-held food direction for the waterfront venue, which gives us a better starting point.</p>\n    <p>Just so I understand, are you still trying to narrow down the food style itself, or is the bigger question now how to structure the flow for 150 guests without it feeling too formal?</p>\n    <p>If it helps, the cleanest next step is a quick call so we can tighten the service direction first and then decide which tasting date makes the most sense for you.</p>\n    <p>I can make time at <strong>10:00 AM</strong>, <strong>11:00 AM</strong>, or <strong>1:00 PM</strong>. Which one feels like the right next move for you?</p>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"margin:28px 0 0;padding:22px;border:1px solid #f1c48a;border-radius:20px;background:#fff8f3;\">\n    <h2 style=\"margin:0 0 12px;color:#7a2f12;font-size:28px;line-height:1.1;\">Come Taste It First</h2>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 12px;color:#6b3b1f;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;\">If tasting makes more sense, I can save you a spot so you can experience the food before deciding from a distance.</p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 8px;color:#3c2415;\"><strong>Date options:</strong> Sunday, May 3 at 5:30 PM<br /><strong></strong>Sunday, May 17 at 2:00 PM<br /><strong></strong>Sunday, May 31 at 2:00 PM</p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 8px;color:#3c2415;\"><strong>Location:</strong> 199 Main St, Fitchburg, MA 01420</p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 18px;color:#3c2415;\"><strong>Code:</strong> ANDRE</p>\n    <div style=\"margin:0 0 18px;display:flex;gap:14px;flex-wrap:wrap;\">\n      <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1V2glKcSbQUtDes3Cuk7Q4bFPiazU1NwT/view\" style=\"display:inline-block;padding:14px 20px;border-radius:999px;background:#f6a313;color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;font-weight:700;\">Tasting Preview</a>\n      <a href=\"https://form.jotform.com/260145767354461\" style=\"display:inline-block;padding:14px 20px;border-radius:999px;background:#16233b;color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;font-weight:700;\">Tasting Registration</a>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"margin:0;color:#6b3b1f;font-size:15px;line-height:1.5;\">The goal first is to get aligned on the call so the tasting actually helps us make the right decision for your event.</p>\n  </div>",
